  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">Mechanism | Add Conjugate Cam FB</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading2">Add Conjugate Cam FB</para>
    <para styleclass="SeeAlso">See <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-Conjugate-Cam-FB">Conjugate-Cam dialog-box</link></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_" style="text-indent:-36px; margin-left:36px;"><toggle type="dropdown" print-expanded="true" help-expanded="false" defaultstyle="false" src-collapsed="tog_plus.gif" src-expanded="tog_minus.gif"><caption><![CDATA[About Conjugate Cams]]></caption></toggle></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="PopupTable2" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Body Table">The design of a cam-system must make sure the Follower (usually a Roller) is in continuous contact with the cam-profile at all machine-speeds. There are two(2) design options:</para>
          <list id="0" type="ol" listtype="upper-alpha" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Bullets" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="Bullets"><text styleclass="VariableName">Force-Closed Cam</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"> - an external force pushes or pulls the </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Follower</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"> against the </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Cam-Profile</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">. E.g. a Spring, Air-Cylinder, Gravity, Magnet, ...</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="VariableName">Body-Closed Cam</text> - a minimum of two(2) <text styleclass="VariableName">Followers</text> in the <text styleclass="VariableName">Follower-Part</text> are in continuous contact with two(2) <text styleclass="VariableName">Cam-Profiles</text> in the <text styleclass="VariableName">Cam-Part</text>. The interactions prevent <text styleclass="Body Text">the </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Followers</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> moving away from from the </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Cam-Profiles</text><text styleclass="Body Text">.</text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Bullets"><text styleclass="VariableName">Body-Closed Cams</text><text styleclass="Body Text Howindent4bullets">, are also called </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Conjugate-Cams</text><text styleclass="Body Text Howindent4bullets">. </text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_">Why do we need to add the Conjugate-Cam FB ?</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">When there is a one </text><text styleclass="Element">2D-Cam</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"> and one Follower, the normal procedure is to select the </text><text styleclass="Element">2D-Cam</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"> as the Power-Source for the Follower-Part. </text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">However, when there are two Cam-Profiles (on one Cam-Part) and two Cam-Followers (on one Follower-Part) - to give a </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Body-Closed Cam</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"> system - &#160;we do not know which of the two Cam and Cam-Follower pairs to select as the Power-Source. The Contact-Force will usually switch between the two Followers throughout the machine-cycle. </text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">In this circumstance, we use a </text><text styleclass="Element-Header">Conjugate-Cam FB</text><text styleclass="Body Text">. </text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text">Then, after</text><text styleclass="Body Text" style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;"> you edit it to select the </text><text styleclass="Element">2D-Cams</text><text styleclass="Body Text" style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;">, the </text><text styleclass="Element">Conjugate-Cam</text><text styleclass="Body Text" style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;"> will be a </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Motor-Element</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> in the</text><text styleclass="Body Text" style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;">&#32;</text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Forces-Configure-Power-Source" styleclass="Body Text" style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;">Configure-Power Source dialog-box</link><text styleclass="Body Text" style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;">, </text></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_">2D-Cam: Elements, Parameters, Analysis, Coordinates</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="1" style="border-width:0px; border-spacing:0px; border-collapse:collapse; cell-border-width:1px; border-color:#993300; border-style:solid; background-color:#ddd6dd;">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <list id="1" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Bullets" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="Bullets">Add a <text styleclass="Element">2D-Cam</text><text styleclass="VariableName"> - &#160;</text><text styleclass="SeeAlso">see </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Command-Add2DCam" styleclass="SeeAlso">Add 2D-Cam</link><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">IF the new <text styleclass="Element">2D-Cam</text> is will be a <text styleclass="VariableName">Conjugate-Cam </text> (<text styleclass="Element">Body-Closed Cam</text>) then</para>
          <list id="2" type="ol" listtype="lower-alpha" formatstring="&#32;&#49;&#46;&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;&#32;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="Interface2">Add</text>&#32;<text styleclass="Element-Header">Conjugate-Cam FB</text> - <text styleclass="SeeAlso">see below</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Body Text">Edit the <text styleclass="Element">Conjugate-Cam FB</text> to add at least two <text styleclass="Element">2D-Cams</text> - <text styleclass="SeeAlso">see </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-Conjugate-Cam-FB" styleclass="SeeAlso">Conjugate-Cam dialog-box</link>. </li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text">Then:</para>
          <list id="3" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="2" styleclass="Body Text" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="Body Text">Select the <text styleclass="Element">2D-Cam</text> (or <text styleclass="Element">Conjugate-Cam FB</text>) &#160;as the <text styleclass="VariableName">Power Source</text> for the <text styleclass="VariableName">Cam-Follower</text> - <text styleclass="SeeAlso">see </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-ConfigurePowerSource" styleclass="SeeAlso">Configure-Power Source</link><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Body Text">Then</para>
          <list id="3" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="2" styleclass="Body Text" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="Body Text">Review the <text styleclass="Element">2D-Cam&apos;s</text> Display, Properties, Cam-Life, and Roller-Life ...<text styleclass="SeeAlso"> - see </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-2DCam" styleclass="SeeAlso">2D-Cam dialog-box</link><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Body Text">Then:</para>
          <list id="4" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="4" styleclass="Bullets" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="Bullets">Add a <text styleclass="Element">Cam-Data FB</text> - <text styleclass="SeeAlso">see </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Command-FB-Cam-Data" styleclass="SeeAlso">Add Cam-Data FB</link><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Bullets"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo">Select a </text><text styleclass="Element">2D-Cam </text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo">to link it to the </text><text styleclass="Element">Cam-Data FB</text><text styleclass="VariableName"> - </text><text styleclass="SeeAlso">see </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Command-FB-Cam-Data" anchor="CAMDATAFB-LINKTO2DCAM" styleclass="SeeAlso">Link the Cam-Data FB to a 2D-Cam</link></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Body Text">Then:</para>
          <list id="5" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="6" styleclass="Bullets" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="Bullets">Analyze 5 different parameters for the <text styleclass="Element">2D-Cam</text><text styleclass="VariableName"> - </text><text styleclass="SeeAlso">see below</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Bullets"><text styleclass="Body Text">Calculate the Cam-Coordinates</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"> - </text><text styleclass="SeeAlso">see </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-FunctionBlock-CamCoordinates" styleclass="SeeAlso">Cam-Coordinates dialog</link><text styleclass="Body Text">&#32;</text></li>
          </list>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
